0th.270: A man holds a cat as members of the Bloomington Fire Department exit a building after a fire at 305 North Pete Ellis Dr., Tuesday, March 19, 2018. The fire was contained to one apartment unit and all three floors of the building were evacuated according to Bloomington Fire Department Battalion Chief Travis Drescher. The cause of the fire is under investigation. (Photo by Jeremy Hogan/The Bloomingtonian)
